gently into that good night.

11:27.788 --> 11:32.257
Hooray, it's settled.
So, cinoman's out,
mellor's in.

11:32.259 --> 11:32.824
Silver lining.

11:32.826 --> 11:36.961
Now we can go make out
in the supply closet
without fear of punishment.

11:36.963 --> 11:37.862
